                },
                "dcterms:description": "The PSDI Index Search provides machine-readable access through the OPTIMADE API to diverse scientific data resources harvested by the PSDI Indexing Service, enabling queries across multiple data sources through a common interface. It facilitates automated workflows, reproducible computational analyses, and large-scale data processing. The indexed resources are also available through the PSDI Cross Data Search, allowing users to search them via a graphical user interface.",
