                        "dcterms:description": "PSDI Data Conversion is your one stop shop for file format conversion. This enables users to seamlessly convert between different file formats and view information about the quality of the proposed conversion. The PSDI Python Library for Data Conversion is available via PyPi and can be installed and run on your own computing infrastructure, enabling you to include a data conversion in your own pipelines. It contains all of the same file conversion functionality of our online service but without the need to upload your data to PSDI and without any restrictions on file sizes.",
