                },
                "dcterms:description": "This resource theme pertains to data and metadata collected during flow battery reproducibility studies that have been conducted by over 30 institutions across the world. A community data collection contains extensive metadata associated with cell assembly and electrochemical testing, whilst a live data dashboard is available for visualising the raw and processed electrochemical data collected by the participants.",
