                        },
                        "dcterms:description": "The Catalysis Data Infrastructure (CDI) Data Objects resource provides access to the UK Catalysis Hub (UKCH) published data objects that support research outputs. Through the CDI Portal, PSDI Cross Data Search and PSDI Index search users can search, explore, and reuse these data resources.\nIn the Catalysis Data Infrastructure (CDI) knowledge graph, data objects are linked with researchers, institutions, publications, and research themes, fostering data discovery, highlighting collaborations, and supporting analysis of data-driven research. CDI Data Objects can be extended to include domain-specific data resources such as chemical entities, materials, or analytical methods.",
