                        },
                        "dcterms:description": "The Catalysis Data Infrastructure (CDI) Publications resource provides access to the UK Catalysis Hub (UKCH) Publications, including peer-reviewed articles, books, and theses. CDI Publications offer a dedicated entry point into the CDI knowledge graph through the CDI Portal. PSDI Cross Data Search and PSDI Index search can be used to explore and analyse research publications.\nWithin CDI, publications are linked to researchers (authors), institutions, research themes, and associated data objects. The linking enhances publication discovery, displays research relationships, and supports insight into research activity. CDI Publications can be expanded to include domain-specific indexes about chemicals, materials, and analysis methods.",
